io.micronaut.core.convert.value

Interface ConvertibleValues<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - The generic value
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Map.Entry<String,V>>, ValueResolver<CharSequence>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConvertibleMultiValues<V>, Cookies, HttpHeaders, HttpParameters, MutableConvertibleMultiValues<V>, MutableConvertibleValues<V>, MutableHttpHeaders, Session
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConvertibleMultiValuesMap, ConvertibleValuesMap, InMemorySession, MutableConvertibleMultiValuesMap, MutableConvertibleValuesMap, NettyCookies, NettyHttpHeaders, NettyHttpParameters, ObjectNodeConvertibleValues

    public interface ConvertibleValues<V>
extends ValueResolver<CharSequence>, Iterable<Map.Entry<String,V>>
    An interface for classes that represent a map-like structure of values that can be converted.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Graeme Rocher
